data.description: Stylish, Updated home near Downtown Spokane & highly sought after Kendall Yards! Clean and updated with new flooring, Romex wiring, double pane windows, newer gas furnace and central AC, sheetrock throughout, cable/internet ready, vinyl siding and more. Expansive main level floor plan with large gathering kitchen, laundry, 3/4 bath, along with space or home office and mud room! Second floor offers 4 well laid out bedrooms *BONUS Primary Bedroom w/ walk in closet & office space* and an updated, stylish full bath. Fully sprinkled corner lot with off street parking on newly poured driveway, 2 car garage and covered patio! Act Fast!
